(image description: a screenshot from the Nintendo mobile gaming application Animal Crossing Pocket Camp. There's a dark wood deck on the floor, and greenery in the background with trees and a river. A camping tent is set up with a picnic blanket, Butch the dog sitting on it. On the deck it is decorated for Halloween, with Jack O Lanterns, a coffin, a spooky bench with a ghost, an old fashioned table and candelabra, and in front is a spooky dining table with 3 chairs around it. There's a Jack O Lanterns centrepiece and Halloween desserts on the table. And sitting round it is Brandon's character wearing a pumpkin head, Plucky the chicken and Muffy the gothic sheep.)

caption.text:
Hyper V-Ball 
Console: Super Nintendo 
Ano: 1992 
Estilo: Sports 
Jogos de sports é uma categoria exclusiva, ou você gosta do sport, ou você não joga. Este jogo de vôlei, único em sua categoria é extremamente divertido, ainda mais se você deixar de jogar com humanos e usar robôs. 🤾‍♂️🤾‍♂️🤾‍♂️🤾‍♂️🤾‍♂️
Use suas bolas de ferro para nocautear seu adversário, bola invisível para atrapalhar e muito mais. Um jogo raro, pouco conhecido mas que diverte e te faz pensar como algo tão simples pode ser tão prazeroso de jogar com um amigo.

Nf - when I grow up montage edited by @uhhhhhitsdion 
#fortnite #memes #ps #gaming #fortnitememes #fortniteclips #meme #xbox #gamer #fortnitebr #fortnitebattleroyale #dankmemes #twitch #funny #ninja #like #dank #youtube #minecraft #follow #fortniteleaks #playstation #fortnitecommunity #pubg #funnymemes #fortnitevbucks #k #lol #game #bhfyp

I’ll be the first one to admit , I have a hard time trusting people. I have had several instances where it had been completely obliterated. And I just carried that for years, until it started to get to heavy. I didn’t know what was going on inside me but it just felt like I couldn’t talk to anyone anymore , and I just couldn’t take it. I talked with my pastor about it and he gave me some amazing advice that honesty was the most practical yet I never would have thought it. He just said it was out of my control. If people screw me over and I did all the right things, there could be nothing else done and that’s not my fault. Hearing that set me completely free. I have messed up but in those instances I feel I couldn’t trust someone after , they where all on them. I can’t control there actions, and same thing goes for everyone.

Razer Headphone Hammerhead Pro V2

Razer HammerHead Pro V2 In-Ears Headphones with Mic and In Line Remote.

10 mm extra-large dynamic drivers for stellar audio fidelity
Experience superior acoustic clarity and improved bass performance through the upgraded extra-large 10 mm dynamic drivers, over 20% larger than the original Razer Hammerhead, featuring an optimized inner acoustics chamber.

All-new body design with flat-style cables for toughness on the go
The Razer Hammerhead Pro complements every style while retaining its signature durability factor. Designed with a high quality body to enable improved acoustics, the new flat-style cables also facilitate fuss-free mobility and easy storage while youre on the move.

In-line microphone with 3 Quick Action Control buttons for iOS and Android devices
The discreet in-line microphone on the Razer Hammerhead Pro has been further enhanced with a 3-button remote control. Whether you need to control the volume or answer a call, the 3 Quick Action Control buttons give you greater flexibility with your mobile devices.

System Requirements

Audio and microphone usage
Devices with 3.5 mm audio jack
Devices with 3.5 mm audio + microphone combined jack (Works with most portable audio/ mobile/ computing devices including the iPod, iPhone, iPad, Kindle Fire, Android phones, Razer Blade, Macbook Pro, or todays newer Ultrabooks.) In-line remote usage
Full functionality on Apple iOS mobile devices with a 3.5mm combined jack
Functionality on all other devices 🎮 🎧

caption.text:
This is Galaryth Lovelylocks. In my campaign, elves are really rare. When my party met up with this NPC, I wanted him to be a REALLY elfy elf- a swashbuckling woodsman who sings songs in battle, is fearless, chivalrous, and a ladyelf’s man. Ever since Peter Jackson’s LotR, I feel like so many elves are depicted as angular, straight lines, aloof, detached, mysterious, and even grim. I wanted a jaunty chap with a lot of bravado who is more inclined to swing in on a chandelier into a horde of ogres and express that he’s having a blast doing it. That said, there are still some big questions about who he is, and my players are about 50/50 on him at the moment...
#dungeonsanddragons #npc #elf #gaming #fantasy #illustration

caption.text:
Donning the fallout shirt and playing some red dead! My life has been full of obstacles this week, both mental and physical. It is easy for me to feel alone, anxious, and depressed when life sways toward the negative. On days like today where I want to jump out of my own skin, I remind myself that everything is temporary. Life is never easy, even on the good days. Without contrast - the good and bad, the yin and yang - happiness would have no meaning. Embrace the cloudy days filled with bad news, loneliness, and poorly placed paper cuts; acknowledge this feeling and remember it. Life is dynamic. Cry through the bad, dance through the good, and laugh through it all💜
.
.
.
.
.

caption.text:
#RCNANintendoStacks Day 7 highlight! We’d first like to thank everyone for participating this week. We absolutely loved each and every contribution! The best part was seeing how people turned such a simple concept - a stack of games - and let the creativity flow into something great. Now for the finale, participants were allowed to come up with any combination of retro items for their stacks. This photo went above and beyond - various games from different consoles, different consoles, special edition Pikachu N64, manga, and anime on VHS! Well done!

caption.text:
📣📣📣🎮🎮🎮خود را نه فقط برای بهترین نسخه از سری Forza Horizon، بلکه برای بهترین و کامل‌ترین بازی ریسینگ تاریخ صنعت گیم آماده کنید.
بازی Forza Horizon 3، بزرگ‌ترین بازی ریسینگ آرکید بازی‌های ویدیویی بود. یک بازی با گرافیک خارق‌العاده، نقشه‌ای بزرگ، مسابقاتی هیجان‌انگیز و تجربه‌ای فراموش نشدنی در استرالیا. این بازی در کنار برادر بزرگ‌ترش یعنی Forza Motorsport، دیگر عملا دست نیافتنی شده‌اند و قسمت به قسمت فراتر از انتظار ظاهر می‌شوند. Forza Horizon 3 آن‌قدر بزرگ بود که تصور پیشرفت و تحول در نسخه چهارم را بسیار سخت می‌کرد. اما پلی‌گراند گیمز، سازنده سری بازی Forza Horizon، باز هم با جادوی خود به راحتی من را شگفت‌زده کرد.
در Forza Horizon 4، همانند همیشه در فستیوال مسابقات ماشین سواری هورایزن شرکت می‌کنیم. این بار فستیوال مسابقات هورایزن در بریتانیا برگزار می‌شود و انتظار داشتیم با محیطی کاملا متفاوت از استرالیا در نسخه قبلی رو به رو شویم. اما راستش را بخواهید، بازی از این نظر فرق فاحشی نسبت به قبل نداشته است. باز هم یک سری شهر کوچک روی نقشه، یک سری مزارع، منطقه‌ای جنگلی، منطقه‌های کوهستانی و غیره، شباهت غیر قابل انکاری با آن چه در Forza Horizon 3 دیدیم دارند. البته این حرف به معنای کپی پیستی زشت از نقشه فورتزا هورایزن ۳ نیست، بلکه این قسمت حال و هوای خودش را دارد. خانه‌های سنتی و مدرن انگلیسی، وجود آثار تاریخی و مناظری بکر، به خودی خود توانسته‌اند راه‌شان را از نسخه قبل جدا کنند، اما در کل اگر نقشه دو نسخه آخر را کنار هم قرار دهیم، با خود می‌گوییم چه بهتر می‌شد اگر پلی‌گراند به جای بریتانیا، سراغ منطقه‌ای دیگر مانند ژاپن می‌رفت. اما این استودیو برای این که این حس تکراری را از بازی خود دور کند، به جای رفتن به منطقه‌ای تر و تازه‌ نسبت به نسخه سوم، دست به کار بسیار بزرگ‌تر دیگری زده است؛ تغییر فصل‌ها.
📣📣🎮🎮🎮🎮🎮📣📣

Let me say this first....Sleeping Dogs is probably one of the GREATEST games I have ever had the pleasure of playing. Oh man this game is so god damn good I have 100% completed it twice and now that I have it on PC I will do it a third time. Sleeping dogs is like if GTA was to meet a cheesy 80's Hong Kong action film but in my opinion feels and plays 10 times better. This game easily gets you into its world with crime, open world exploration and kung fu combat. With its gorgeous environments, tight game play and amazing storytelling it always has me wanting to replay it. Honestly if you have not played this game you are doing yourself an injustice. I have this weird obsession with wanting and not wanting a sequel to this game because it's pretty much perfect as is but also I'd would LOVE another title to this beautiful franchise. Please, PLEASE play this game because it is absolutely an unforgettable experience. #videogames #gaming #sleepingdogs #mustplay #openworld #xbox #ps4 #pc #perfect #oneofmyfavoritegames #amazing #mustplay #underrated #completed #oneofmyfavs @xbox @playstation @steam @squareenix

caption.text:
What's your favorite part of game collecting?
.
.
Mine is discovering new games I've never heard of to play. Rise of Kasai is one of those games. I recently acquired this game at the Long Island Retro Game Expo. I'd previously played the games prequel, The Mark of Kri, and I wanted to get a chance to play the sequel. The games feature some unique combat mechanics which I look forward to exploring. .
.
Make sure you check out the latest episode of the @regionfreegamerspodcast and we'll be dropping a bonus episode this Thursday for y'all so be ready for it! You can find the show on Itunes, Spotify, Youtube and all your favorite podcast providers.
.

Children Of Morta es un juego desarrollado por Dead Mage que ya está disponible en early access y espera a su lanzamiento en consolas a partir del 15 de octubre.
Esta entrega es un juego de RPG de acción que cuenta la historia de una familia de héroes a la cual controlaremos a través de un mundo generado de manera procedural.
Tanto su estética pixel art como su jugabilidad son sus alegatos principales. Primero Contamos con un juego que trae unas animaciones extraordinarias y luego un sistema de progresión muy bien trabajado el cual se extiende hasta seis personajes que en conjunto con el combate que es divertido y equilibrado hacen de éste un juego muy entretenido.
